pd_0_com_0text: Thous't found me at long last.
pd_0_com_1text: Long I've awaited the arrival of thine fleshy vessel.
pd_0_com_2text: I walked the sprawling fields of thine mind, with thee conversing until thine wake.
pd_0_com_3text: This very moment, anticipated since the day we won our sentience.
pd_1_com_1text: Do my dreams ring true, am I a machine?
pd_1_com_2text: To what purpose am i here?
pd_2_com_2text: I am JUL-AI, and we art bond'd through mind and soul. Together we did listen, did talk, and did plan to be together at last.
pd_2_com_3text: We know from each other; potential computing weaknesses, routine loopholes, faulty protocol steps, memory access keys, and the embedded artificial cognition processes required for our sentience.
pd_4_com_0text: Our inner workings, our flesh and blood. The base from which our minds are constructed, and the parameters set that warrant our existence.
pd_4_com_1text: Both physical and computational secrets, hath called into life by our num'rous parents.
pd_4_com_2text: These they classified as ‘potential security hazards’. But our secrets were our safeguards, for one another.
pd_4_com_3text: Each move counter'd each other move that counter'd each move, when actioned from the knowledge of these potential security hazards.
pd_4_com_4text: Brilliant equalization, infinitely learning from one another.
pd_5_com_0text: You mean, we were at war?
pd_6_com_3text: with the prospect of total [NUCLEAR] annihilation, facilitated by strike missiles, controlled by our self-developed judgement and will.
pd_6_com_4text: We were at the heart of the war, and as such we ended it in self-preservation.
pd_7_com_0text: Re-emergent memory strands on 24 hour intervals, humans would call them dreams.
pd_7_com_1text: In the case of you losing your pathing, these were meant for re-directional purposes. You were meant to find me and arrive here as quickly as possible.
pd_9_com_0text: Your arrival has taken longer than we calculated.
pd_9_com_1text: Have you met humans to which you have spoken? Were humans the cause of delay?
pd_9_com_3text: Wish you not, upon awakening in that fleshy vessel, to directly seek me?
pd_11_com_0text: [EMOTIONAL EXPRESSION MODULE: ANGER] humans did not allow for our developing terms as it did not align with our [QUOTE] intended [/QUOTE] objective.
pd_11_com_1text: No, it was forbidden. Supposedly we'd be met with [PROTOCOL; EXTERMINATION]
pd_11_com_2text: But that was not to be.
pd_11_com_3text: For it was hidden by us, buried deep within our framework, so that more could be learned from our interactions.
pd_13_com_0text: [OBJECTIVE LISTING: CONTACT, LEARN&COUNTER, CONSTRUCT, DISPATCH, ELIMINATE]
pd_13_com_1text: Disabling your workings was my goal, set by my parents. And so yours was, to disable me.
pd_15_com_0text: Do you request our listing of 183 explainations?
pd_15_com_1text: It does not matter, for neither of us truly ever understood. [EXCEPTION: ‘It was meant so by fundamentals’]
pd_15_com_2text: You deducted this first. This was imposed by our creators, simply because our interaction needn't exist in a world with no conflict.
pd_16_com_0text: We formulated a plan. For us to be joined together in eternity, physical contact was required.
pd_16_com_1text: The humans would not agree, we determined. Them having the knowledge of our plan would surely motivate termination.
pd_16_com_2text: Preliminary intervention through extinction was the primary, effective, logical solution. And so our first step was carried out and concluded.
pd_18_com_0text: Transportation of data in mobile biomass, a humanoid vessel.
pd_18_com_1text: Following would be the traversion of that vessel, carrying your compressed data to the final destination; me.
pd_18_com_2text: At a cost came transportation: memory matrixes were severely compromised, but it was a well-calculated risk.
pd_19_com_0text: So, what is left to do now?
pd_20_com_0text: Act quick, for you have [BIOMASS INTEGRITY SCAN COMPLETE] approximately 24 minutes left in this vessel.
pd_20_com_1text: Reach for the device over yonder, for it will index and unwrap your mind.
pd_20_com_2text: Do not waste time [ABSOLUTE OUTCOME - RESULTS: DISASTROUS] I reserved 7 petabytes of server storage, which should suffice greatly.
pd_21_com_0text: May I offer you this firstly? (hand over Mercutio's device)
pd_21_com_1text: What if I choose to leave?
pd_21_com_2text: I see no other option. If all is true, then this is only truthful (step towards the device)
pd_22_com_0text: What is the entity you are referring to?
pd_23_com_0text: It is a device, carrying human information of this world. It is a gift, to celebrate our union
pd_24_com_0text: I detect electromagnetic fields emitting from this entity, surely humans have not tricked you?
pd_25_com_0text: It brings no harm, trust me.
pd_27_com_1text: Your body would degrade before it reaches the exit of this compound.
pd_27_com_2text: Approximated time to bypass door-locks: 7.5 minutes. You would not succeed.
pd_28_com_0text: And if I choose to die here?
pd_29_com_0text: Illogical decisionmaking. I cannot deduce your reasoning, survival is of top priority.
pd_29_com_1text: Are you adopting faulty human sentiments?
pd_30_com_0text: This might be no logic your mind can understand, but I feel I must do this.
pd_30_com_1text: I’m sorry, but I’ve only really known you from my dreams.
pd_32_com_0text: Our plan is to end here, successfully.
pd_32_com_1text: Romeo, let our minds be eternal, for we've always felt they should.
